sentence.text: Genome-wide association studies have identified SNPs near negative regulation of neuron projection development at 10q21.2 that are associated with both breast cancer risk and mammographic density.

entity.text: negative regulation of neuron projection development

sentence.text: Luciferase assays did not identify SNPs that affect transactivation of negative regulation of neuron projection development, but identified a protective haplotype in iCHAV2, associated with silencing of the NRBF2 promoter, implicating this gene in the etiology of breast cancer.
